


Secrets have new line at the end 
===============

echo "password" | tr -d \\n | base64 -w 0

===============
Fixes the issues

********* Sample shell ********
#!/bin/sh

echo " ***encoded...$1"
echo "$1" | tr -d \\n | base64 -w 0

echo "\n\n===================="

echo "\n\n===================="
echo "\ndecoded..."
echo "$1" | base64 -d
echo ""
